        <td>Animal Whistle</td>
        <td><a href="/hobbity/appendix/pcs/wedge/">Wedge</a></td>
        <td>Bought from <a href="/hobbity/appendix/npcs/#farmer-fallow">Farmer Fallow</a> — <a href="/hobbity/stories/2025-11-06-the-gomwick-harvest-festival/#the-old-road-to-gomwick">The Gomwick Harvest Festival</a></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Mysterious Stockings</td>
